# Secrets and documentation

This repo is **public**. Do not expose infrastructure credentials in markdown, skills, code comments, or examples.

## Gitignored (real values only)

- `.env`
- `aws-postgres.env` — `ELASTIC_IP`, `DB_PASSWORD`, instance IDs
- `*.pem` — SSH keys

## Docs and examples — placeholders only

| Use | Not |
|-----|-----|
| `<ELASTIC_IP>` | Real Elastic IP from `aws-postgres.env` |
| `PASSWORD` / `change-me` | Real database or admin passwords |
| `https://kuchup.com` | `http://<real-ip>/...` |
| `postgresql://relocation:PASSWORD@<ELASTIC_IP>:5432/...` | Full live `DATABASE_URL` |

**OK:** `127.0.0.1`, `localhost`, `172.17.0.1` (Docker bridge), public domain names.

See [`engineering-standards`](../.claude/skills/engineering-standards/SKILL.md) §7 and [`docs/reference/rules.md`](../../docs/reference/rules.md#secrets-and-documentation).
